<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - University Management System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-policy-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .privacy-policy-container h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .privacy-policy-container p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .privacy-policy-container h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-policy-container .effective-date {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="privacy-policy-container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="effective-date">Effective date: October 19, 2023</p>
        <p>At University Management System, your privacy is of utmost importance to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p>We collect information that you provide directly to us, such as when you enroll in courses, use our services, or interact with the University Management System. This may include your name, email address, phone number, academic records, and payment information.</p>

        <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to provide, maintain, and improve our services, process transactions, manage academic records, respond to inquiries, and communicate with you about updates and promotions.</p>

        <h2>3. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. We may share data with university staff and faculty to facilitate your academic experience.</p>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. Our system uses advanced security protocols to ensure the safety of your data.</p>

        <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on our website. We encourage you to review our privacy policy whenever you use our services to stay informed about how we protect the information we collect.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
